#. Tag: title
#: usermenu.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "User-Configurable Menu"
msgstr "Korisnički podesiv meni"

#. Tag: title
#: usermenu.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Postavke"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:7
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile; supports a user-configurable menu, which will appear as a part of "
"&kile;'s menu. This menu can be configured using &kile;'s configuration "
"dialog with <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure "
"Kile</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>User Menu</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"&kile; podržava korisnički podesiv meni, koji će se pojaviti kao dio &kile; "
"menija. Ovaj meni može se podesiti koristeći &kile; konfiguracijski dialog "
"sa <menuchoice><guimenu>Postavke</guimenu><guisubmenu>Konfiguracije Kile</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Korisnički meni</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Configure the user menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Konfigurisati korisnički meni</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Configure the user menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfigurisati korisnički meni</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "You have two options where to place this menu:"
msgstr "Imate dvije opcije gdje da postavite ovaj meni:"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"either the menu <guimenu>User Menu</guimenu> will appear in the main menu "
"bar between the menus <guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu> and <guimenu>Wizard</guimenu> "
"and the configuration wizard <guimenuitem>Edit User Menu</guimenuitem> in "
"the <guimenu>Wizard</guimenu> menu"
msgstr ""
"ili će se meni <guimenu>Korisnički meni</guimenu> pojaviti u glavnoj meni "
"traci između menija <guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu> i <guimenu>Čarobnjak</guimenu> "
"i konfiguracijski čarobnjak <guimenuitem>Uredi korisnički meni</guimenuitem> "
"u <guimenu>Čarobnjak</guimenu> meniju"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>User Menu is placed in the main menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Korisnički meni je smješten u glavnom meniju</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>User Menu is placed in the main menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Korisnički meni je smješten u glavnom meniju</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"or both items will appear at the bottom of the <guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu> menu."
msgstr "ili će se obje stavke pojaviti na dnu <guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu> menija."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>User Menu as a part of the LaTeX menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Korisnički meni kao dio LaTeX menija</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>User Menu as a part of the LaTeX menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Korisnički meni kao dio LaTeX menija</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Already existing user-defined tags from older versions of &kile; are "
"automatically transformed into the new user-configurable menu. The tags are "
"saved in a file called <filename>usertags.xml</filename> and like all menu "
"definition files, they can be found in the local user menu directory of "
"&kile;: <filename>KILE_APP_DIR/usermenu/</filename>, &eg; <filename>/home/"
"user/.kde/share/apps/kile/usermenu/</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Već postojeće korisnički-definisane oznake sa starijih verzija &kile; se "
"automatski transformišu u nove korisnički podesive menije. Oznake su spašene "
"u fajlu koji se zove <filename>usertags.xml</filename> i kao svi fajlovi "
"definisanja menija, mogu se naći u lokalnom korisničkom direktoriju &kile;: "
"<filename>KILE_APP_DIR/usermenu/</filename>, &eg; <filename>/home/user/.kde/"
"share/apps/kile/usermenu/</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use different menu definition files for different tasks. Call the "
"user menu wizard <menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</guimenu><guisubmenu>Edit User "
"Menu</guisubmenu></menuchoice> or <menuchoice><guimenu>LaTeX</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Edit User Menu</guisubmenu></menuchoice> to install or "
"edit a menu definition file."
msgstr ""
"Možete koristiti različite fajlove definisanja menija za različite zadatke. "
"Pozovite čarobnjaka za korisnički meni <menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Edit User Menu</guisubmenu></menuchoice> or "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu><guisubmenu>Edit User Menu</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> za instalaciju ili uređenje fjla za definisanje menija."

#. Tag: title
#: usermenu.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wizard"
msgstr "Čarobnjak"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can create new or change existing menus with a comfortable user menu "
"configuration wizard found at <menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Edit User Menu</guisubmenu></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Možete kreirati nove ili mijenjati postojeće menije sa ugodnim čarobnjakom "
"za konfiguraciju korisničkog menija, koji se nalazi na "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</guimenu><guisubmenu>Uredi korisnički meni</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>User Menu Wizard</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Čarobnjak korisničkog menija</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>User Menu Wizard</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Čarobnjak korisničkog menija</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left side you will see an existing menu-tree. Like a standard menu, "
"three different kinds of menu items are available:"
msgstr ""
"Na lijevoj strani vidjet će te postojeće stablo menija. Kao kod standardnog "
"menija, tri različite vrste stavki menija su dostupne:"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "standard menu entries, which are assigned to an action"
msgstr "standardni unosi menija, koji su dodjeljeni radnji"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "submenus, which contain more menu items"
msgstr "podmeniji, koji sadrže više stavki menija"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "separators, to get a visible structure of all entries."
msgstr "rastavljači, da se dobije vidljiva struktura svih unosa."

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To modify this menu, use the six buttons on the left side. More possible "
"actions are available in the context menu of already existing menu items."
msgstr ""
"Da modifikujete ovaj meni, koristite šest dugmadi sa lijeve strane. Više "
"mogućih radnji je dostupno u dodatnom meniju već postojećih stavki menija."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>User-Defined Menutree</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Korsinički definisano stablo menija</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>User-Defined Menutree</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Korsinički definisano stablo menija</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each standard menu item is assigned to one of three action types, where each "
"of them has different attributes, which could be set:"
msgstr ""
"Svaka standardna stavka menija je dodjeljena jednoj od tri vrste radnji, "
"gdje svaka od njih ima različite atribute, koji se mogu postaviti:"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Text:</guilabel>&nbsp; &kile; gives you the ability to make your "
"own tags. A tag is similar to a shortcut that launches some command or "
"writes frequently-used texts, &eg; Joe Sixpack often uses the sentences "
"<userinput>Hi, I have been inserted ...</userinput>. This tag will be "
"inserted at the current cursor position, when this action is called (see "
"above). Metachars are also available (see <xref linkend="
"\"id_usermenu_placeholders\" role=\"select: title pageabbrv\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Text:</guilabel>&nbsp; &kile; daje vam mogućnost da napravite "
"vlastite oznage. Oznaka je slična prečici koja pokreće neku komandu ili "
"ispisuje često korišteni tekst, &eg; Joe Sixpack često koristi rečenice "
"<userinput>Ćao, ja sam ubačen...</userinput>. Ova oznaka će biti ubačena na "
"trenutnu pozciju kursora, kada se ova akcija pozove (vidi iznad). "
"Metaznakovi su također dostupni (see <xref linkend=\"id_usermenu_placeholders"
"\" role=\"select: title pageabbrv\"/>)."

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Insert file contents:</guilabel>&nbsp; Inserts the complete "
"contents of a given file."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ubaci sadržaj fajla:</guilabel>&nbsp; Ubacuje kompletan sadržaj "
"datog fajla."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Insert file contents</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Ubaci sadržaj fajla</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Insert file contents</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Ubaci sadržaj fajla</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Execute an external program:</guilabel>&nbsp; The output of this "
"program can be inserted into the opened document. Metachar <userinput>%M</"
"userinput> is also possible in the command line of this program, as the "
"selected text will be saved in a temporary file. Use <userinput>%M</"
"userinput> for the filename of this temporary file."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Izvrši vanjski program:</guilabel>&nbsp; Izlaz ovog programa može "
"biti ubačen u otvoren dokument. Metaznak <userinput>%M</userinput> je "
"također moguć u komandnoj liniji ovog programa, pošto će selektovani tekst "
"biti spašen u privremeni fajl. Koristi <userinput>%M</userinput> za ime ovog "
"privremenog fajla."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Execute an external program</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izvrši vanjski program</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Execute an external program</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izvrši vanjski program</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If some important information for an action is missing, menu items are "
"colored red. This may be a nonexisting file"
msgstr ""
"Ako neka bitna informacija za radnju nedostaje, stavke menija su obojene u "
"crveno. Ovo može biti nepostojeći fajl"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Nonexisting file</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nepostojeći fajl</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Nonexisting file</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nepostojeći fajl</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"or a missing title for the menu entry, which will be shown with question "
"marks as <userinput>???</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"ili nedostaje naziv za unos menija, koji će biti prikazan sa znakom upitnika "
"<userinput>???</userinput>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Missing title of a menu entry</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nedostaje naziv unešenog menija</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Missing title of a menu entry</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nedostaje naziv unešenog menija</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you open the context menu of such a red colored menu item, you will get "
"an additional option for more information concerning this error."
msgstr ""
"Ako otvorite dodatni meni takve crvene stavke menija, dobit će te dodatne "
"opcije za više informacija koje se tiču ove greške."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Additional info</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Dodatne informacije</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Additional info</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Dodatne informacije</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More information may also be available using the <guilabel>What's this</"
"guilabel> feature of most widgets."
msgstr ""
"Više informacija može biti dostupno i koristeći <guilabel>Šta je ovo</"
"guilabel> svojstvo mnogih widgets."

#. Tag: title
#: usermenu.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Placeholders"
msgstr "Automatski popunjeno"

#. Tag: title
#: usermenu.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert Text"
msgstr "Unesi tekst"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are some placeholders you can use in your user-defined tags: "
"<userinput>%C</userinput>, <userinput>%B</userinput>, <userinput>%M</"
"userinput>, <userinput>%E</userinput>, <userinput>%R</userinput> and "
"<userinput>%T</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Postoje neki placeholders koje možete vidjeti u vašim korsinički "
"definisatnim oznakama <userinput>%C</userinput>, <userinput>%B</userinput>, "
"<userinput>%M</userinput>, <userinput>%E</userinput>, <userinput>%R</"
"userinput> and <userinput>%T</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>%C</userinput>:&nbsp; this is where the cursor will be placed "
"after the insertion of a user-defined tag."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>%C</userinput>:&nbsp; ovo je gdje će kursor biti postavljen nakon "
"ubacivanja korisnički definisane oznake."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Cursor Position (%C)</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pozicija kursora (%C)</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Cursor Position (%C)</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pozicija kursora (%C)</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>%B</userinput>:&nbsp; will be replaced by a bullet (see <xref "
"linkend=\"editing_bullets\" role=\"select: title pageabbrv\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>%B</userinput>:&nbsp; će biti zamjenjena bulletom (see <xref "
"linkend=\"editing_bullets\" role=\"select: title pageabbrv\"/>)."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Bullet (%B)</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Bullet (%B)</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Bullet (%B)</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Bullet (%B)</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>%M</userinput>:&nbsp; will be replaced by the selected text."
msgstr "<userinput>%M</userinput>:&nbsp; bit će zamjenjeno označenim tekstom."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Selected Text (%M)</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>označeni tekst (%M)</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Selected Text (%M)</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Označeni tekst (%M)</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>%E</userinput>:&nbsp; denotes the indentation depth of text "
"inside an environment."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>%E</userinput>:&nbsp; označava dubinu uvlačenja teksta unutar "
"okruženja."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Indentation of environment text (%E)</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Uvlačenje teksta okruženja (%E)</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Indentation of environment text (%E)</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Uvlačenje teksta okruženjat (%E)</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>%R</userinput>:&nbsp; will call a reference-dialog to choose a "
"label which has already been defined. This can be used to refer to a "
"predefined label, which you can choose from a drop-down list (see also "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu><guimenuitem>References</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>ref</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu><guimenuitem>References</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>pageref</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>%R</userinput>:&nbsp; pozvat će obavještajni prozor da se izabere "
"oznaka koja je već definisana. Ovo se može korisititi da se uputi na već "
"predefinisanu oznaku, koju možete izabrati sa padajuće liste (see also "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu><guimenuitem>References</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>ref</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu><guimenuitem>References</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>pageref</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>References (%R)</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Reference (%R)</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>References (%R)</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Reference (%R)</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>%T</userinput>:&nbsp; will call a citation-dialog to choose an "
"already defined citation. The same as using <menuchoice><guimenu>LaTeX</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>References</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>cite</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> a list with all the citation keys pops up."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>%T</userinput>:&nbsp; pozvat će citirajući prozor da se izabere "
"već definisani citat. Isto kao korištenje <menuchoice><guimenu>LaTeX</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>References</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>cite</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>iskoče liste sa svim citatima."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Citation Keys (%T)</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Citiranje (%T)</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Citation Keys (%T)</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Citiranje (%T)</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let's consider another example, with the following macro <userinput>"
"\\frac{%M}{%C}</userinput>. First, we select a number in our text, let's say "
"<userinput>42</userinput>. Now we invoke this macro and obtain <userinput>"
"\\frac{42}{}</userinput> with the cursor located within the second pair of "
"brackets."
msgstr ""
"Razmotrimo još jedan primjer, sa sljedećim macro <userinput>\\frac{%M}{%C}</"
"userinput>. Prvo, selektujemo broj u našem tekstu, na primjer <userinput>42</"
"userinput>. Sada pozovemo ovaj macro and dobijemo <userinput>\\frac{42}{}</"
"userinput> sa kursorom lociranim unutar drugog para zagrada."

#. Tag: title
#: usermenu.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert File Contents"
msgstr "Umetni sadržaj datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to insert the contents of a text file, you could use the same "
"placeholders."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite da ubacite sadržaj tekstualnog fajla, možete korsititi iste "
"placeholders."

#. Tag: title
#: usermenu.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Execute A Program"
msgstr "Izvrši program"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to execute an external program, only the <userinput>%M</"
"userinput> for selected text is recognized in the command line. The "
"selection will be saved in a temporary file and the placeholder <userinput>"
"%M</userinput> is replaced with this filename."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite da izvršite vanjski program, samo <userinput>%M</userinput> samo "
"za selektovani tekst je prepoznat u komandnoj liniji. Označeno će biti "
"spašeno u privremeni fajl i placeholder <userinput>%M</userinput>je "
"zamjenjen sa ovim nazivom."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Execute an external program (%M)</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izvrši vanjski program (%M)</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Execute an external program (%M)</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izvrši vanjski program (%M)</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another placeholder is <userinput>%S</userinput>, which is replaced by the "
"complete base name of the current document without the path. This base name "
"consists of all characters in the file up to (but not including) the last "
"'.' character."
msgstr ""
"Još jedan placeholder je <userinput>%S</userinput>, koji je zamjenjen sa "
"kompletnim baznim imenom trenutnog dokumenta bez staze. Ovo bazno ime "
"sastoji se od svih znakova u fajlu do (ali ne uključujući) zadnje '.' znaka."

#. Tag: title
#: usermenu.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameter"
msgstr "Parametar"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most menu entries may have additional self-explaining parameters, which may "
"be checked. If some of these parameters are not available for some kind of "
"action, they are disabled."
msgstr ""
"Većina unosa menija može sadržavati dodatne parametre za objašnjenje, koji "
"se mogu provjeriti. Ako neki od ovih parametara nisu dostuoni u nekoj vrsti "
"radnje, oni su onemogućeni."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>User Menu Parameter</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Parametar korsiničkog menija</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>User Menu Parameter</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Parametar korsiničkog menija</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:349
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here is one example for executing an external program:"
msgstr "Evo jedan primjer za izvršavanje vanjskog programa:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Parameter example</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Primjer parametra</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Parameter example</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Primjer parametra</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can see that a <userinput>perl</userinput> script is called, which "
"should work with current selection. The <guilabel>Needs selected text</"
"guilabel> parameter is checked to assure a selection. The output of this "
"script will be inserted (<guilabel>Insert the output of the chosen program</"
"guilabel>) and replace the current selection (<guilabel>Replace selected "
"text</guilabel>), but not selected itself."
msgstr ""
"Možete vidjeti da <userinput>perl</userinput> skripta je pozvana, što bi "
"trebalo raditi sa trenutnom oznakom. The <guilabel>Needs selektirani tekst</"
"guilabel> parametar je provjeren da osigura selekciju. Izlaz ove skripte će "
"biti ubačen(<guilabel>Insert the output of the chosen program</guilabel>) i "
"označiti treuntnu selekciju (<guilabel>Replace selected text</guilabel>), "
"ali neće sam označiti."

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Of course you can also call your own programs or scripts. For example select "
"a list of numbers, separated by spaces, and call a script or Perl program, "
"which transforms this selection into &latex; code for a matrix. Whatever "
"your ideas may be, you can realize them using the following usermenu entry."
msgstr ""

