#. Tag: title
#: usermenu.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Menu Definition Files</title>"
msgstr "<title>Definisani fajlovi menija</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can install different menus at runtime for different tasks. When you "
"call the user menu wizard, the current menu definition file is loaded. If "
"you modify it and close the dialog with <guibutton>OK</guibutton>, your "
"changes will be saved and installed as the new user menu. Closing the dialog "
"with <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> will discard all changes."
msgstr ""
"Možete instalirati različite menije tokom rada za različite zadatke. Kada "
"pozovete čarobnjaka za korisnički meni, trenutni definicijski fajl menija se "
"učita. Ako ga modifikujete i zatvorite prozor sa <guibutton>OK</guibutton>, "
"vađe promjene će biti spašene i instalirane kao novi korisnički meni. "
"Zatvaranje prozora sa <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> će odbaciti sve izmjene."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermenu.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Menu Definition Files</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Definisani fajlovi menija</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermenu.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Menu Definition Files</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Definisani fajlovi menija</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You are also free to save the modified file in the user menu directory or to "
"load another menu definition file and install it. All user menu definition "
"files must be saved in the local user menu directory of &kile;: "
"<filename>KILE_APP_DIR/usermenu/</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Također ste slobodni da spasite modifikovani fajl u direktorij korisničkog "
"menija ili da učitate drugi definicijski fajl menija i instalirate ga. Svi "
"definicijski fajlovi menija se moraju spasiti u lokalni direktorij "
"korisničkog menija &kile;: <filename>KILE_APP_DIR/usermenu/</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: usermenu.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Look at the example menu definition file <userinput>example.xml</userinput> "
"to see more menu entries with their parameters."
msgstr ""
"Pogledajte primjer definisanog fajla menija <userinput>example.xml</"
"userinput> da vidite više unosa sa njihovim parametrima."
